reports.title: Top 100 connected users
reports.query: MATCH (u:User)-[e]->(t:User) RETURN u,e,t,count(e) as degree ORDER BY degree DESC LIMIT 100

reports.title: Top 10 contributors post composition
reports.query:
MATCH (u:User)-[e]->(t:Tweet)
RETURN u.username as Username, COUNT(t) as num_tweets, t.sentiment_label as sentiment ORDER BY num_tweets DESC LIMIT 20

reports.title: Distribution of top negative tweets
reports.query:
MATCH (au:User)<-[e]-(u:User)-[:Tweeted]->(t:Tweet {sentiment_label: 'negative'}) 
RETURN au,e,u,t.sentiment_score as degree ORDER BY degree DESC LIMIT 500

reports.title: Top 10 contributors to negative posts
reports.query:
MATCH (u:User)-[e]->(t:Tweet{sentiment_label:'negative'})
RETURN u.username as Username, COUNT(t) as num_tweets ORDER BY num_tweets DESC LIMIT 20

reports.title: Score against number of comments
reports.query:
MATCH (r:Reddit_post WHERE r.score > 30 and r.score < 10000)
RETURN  r.score as Score, r.comms_num as Number_of_comments 
ORDER BY Score DESC

reports.title: Top contributors
reports.query:
MATCH (u:RUser)-[e]->(r:Reddit_post)
RETURN u.username as Username, COUNT(r) as num_reddits ORDER BY num_reddits DESC LIMIT 20

reports.title: Users with top posts
reports.query:
MATCH (u:RUser)-[e]->(r:Reddit_post)
RETURN u.username as Username, r.score as score ORDER BY score DESC LIMIT 20

reports.title: Select Twitter User
reports.query:
MATCH (n:`User`) 
WHERE toLower(toString(n.`username`)) CONTAINS toLower($input) 
RETURN DISTINCT n.`username` as value,  n.`username` as display ORDER BY size(toString(value)) ASC LIMIT 5
